            <title>[GROOVY-4781] @WithReadLock and @WithWriteLock creates the wrong locks</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4781</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The @WithReadLock forces a method to obtain a write lock. &lt;br/&gt;
The @WithWriteLock forces a method to obtain a read lock. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is exactly backwards. It should be the other way around. I have a fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
